    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1866-08-08T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1866-08-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="133" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d133">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. King</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Seward</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 62.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Rome,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1866-08-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">August</hi> 8, 1866</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> * * * * * * * *</p>
                <p>I availed myself of the opportunity to repeat to the cardinal the
                            information communicated to me by St. Marie in regard to John H.
                            Surratt. His Eminence was greatly interested by it, and intimated that
                            if the American government desired the surrender of the criminal there
                            would probably be no difficulty in the way.</p>
                <p rend="center">* * * * * * *</p>
                <p>I am, sir, very respectfully, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>RUEUS KING.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward,</hi>
                        <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State, Washington, D. C.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
